_sText:
The 3.0 versions of this map, making a huge transition from previous versions, comes to you with many upgrades attached.

This map I would consider 3 levels, the normal start level, a subterranean level including death fans, and the upper levels which sport the two large fans which you can walk on.

This was my first map ever made, but comes to you in a revised version which should increase the fun of this map.
